data.description: Introducing this charming 2,063 square foot home nestled in a serene community. Boasting four spacious bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms, this residence offers ample space for comfortable living. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting interior that seamlessly combines modern aesthetics with functionality. Outside, a fenced yard provides privacy and security, making it an ideal space for outdoor activities and family fun. Beyond the home, the community offers a range of amenities, including a beautiful pool for hot summer days, a basketball court for active recreation, and a playground for the young ones to enjoy. Close to shopping, restaurants, Tampa Premium Outlet Mall, Wiregrass Mall, hospitals, colleges, highways and Florida’s first lagoon Epperson Lagoon.  This home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and community amenities, making it an ideal place to call home for families and individuals alike. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful property yours.
